doppel.name: Doppel of Fever
doppel.title: Feature: Tube
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel is entranced by the beauty of her own Doppel, but has yet to realize that it is still hiding its true form. It attacks from where it sprouts out of her back, using a large projection of itself made from the hardened paint (Pathogen Tempera) it emits. It boasts a Witch-like figure as it does this, despite its Doppel nature — this is because its human body becomes so coated in paint that she's no longer visible. The master cannot verify the appearance of her Doppel, but apparently it is "just as beautiful when you view it from the inside".

cardSkill.name: Melt into my Artwork
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [VIII] / Guaranteed Bewitch / Guaranteed Poison / Stun Chance

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who is trying to create a world where no one has to become a Witch, Alina is an artistic genius obsessed with life and death who pours herself into her work, dreaming of making masterpieces featuring Witches themselves. She's used herself as a subject for her art when in a creative slump.

charaMessageList.message: All I want to see is the best art ever made!

That girl's beloved manga,
it's just as ridicolo as she is.
No...this isn't right... No, not at all!
I myself will be my final masterpiece!
Che palle! Still alive…

I, Alina,
will NEVER concede to artist's block!

If you're going to lie to yourself,
you might as well be dead.
Oh, I just got so excited...
*Sigh* I, Alina, have grown tired of this...
I could never get tired of this.
You are not worthy to be used in my artwork.

cardMagia.name: Infinite Poseidon

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [IX] / Charges MP / Accele MP UP (Self/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Transformation
doppel.title: Feature: Glass Slipper
doppel.description: The master of this emotion uses its power to their utmost content. This Doppel enhances the transforming ability of its possessor manyfold, allowing her to transform into someone else for a certain amount of time. The result of this transformation is truer to the ideal image of the person than the actual person it is based on. However, because the transformation is so perfect, if it is used too much, the user is likely to lose track of their own identity. It turns the user into the ideal state of its target, so it sometimes appears slightly different from the original.

cardSkill.name: Here I Am Again to Help You
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [IX] / Accele MP UP [IX] / Critical Hit Chance [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who has trouble opening up to others. Rena acts cocky to make up for her lack of self-confidence, which leads people who don't know her well to misunderstanding her. She's a picky eater and loves sweets. She is also a big fan of idols.

charaMessageList.message: Oh, Momoko... What're you doing now?!
O-okay then... Become my servant!
I'm back to being alone...
Hehe...I love this concert DVD!
You're the one who started this fight!!
Even I hate me...
I told you! I'm not mad at you at all!!
This result seems quite natural to me, y'know?
You're not bad.
This is all thanks to you. Thank you.
It's definitely high five time!

selectableCharaList.name: Momoko Togame

cardMagia.name: The Universe's Edge
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [V] / Damage After Using Charge UP (Team/3 Turns)

cardSkill.name: So What If I'm Overbearing?!
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [VII] / Damage After Using Charge UP [VII] / Ignore Defense

cardMagia.name: The Universe's Edge
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [VII] / Damage After Using Charge UP / Blast Damage UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [IX] / Damage After Using Charge UP / Blast Damage UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Self Discipline
doppel.title: Feature: Nails
doppel.description: The master of this emotion cares not where its power fly. This Doppel attacks with its huge fingers, along with the many fingers that fly around it. All the nails on the fingers are polished and decorated. It cares very much about its nails. When someone praises them, it becomes quite happy, but when someone says something bad about them, it gets discouraged and depressed. It is quite troublesome to deal with when this happens, so it is a good idea to let it attack the enemy as soon as you summon it.

cardSkill.name: So What If I'm Overbearing?!
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [IX] / Damage After Using Charge UP [IX] / Ignore Defense

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who is always looking out for rookies. The middle child, Momoko was influenced by her two brothers' boyishness, but she loves cute, girly things like stuffed animals. Because she loves cute things she's also a fan of female idols.

charaMessageList.message: Is it wrong? I love idols!
Why'd I become a Magical Girl again…?

Call me a meddler if you want.
I can't just ignore this!
Me likin' somethin' like this…it's weird, huh?
Why've I grown into such a tough girl?
My team's well-balanced! Don't you think?
Aww...I always have the worst timing!
Neat and clean, just the way I like it!
It's all about team work, right?
I'm countin' on you to back me up from here on!
All of us are here! It was bound to turn out like this.

selectableCharaList.name: Karin Misono

cardMagia.name: Candy Death Squall
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [V] / DEF DOWN (Target/3 Turns) / Accele MP UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Larceny
doppel.title: Feature: Mortsafe
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel is cowardly by nature, which is why she gave birth to this stubborn Doppel. It fears losing anything and is fixated on obtaining more. It shares its proclivity for thievery with its master, and will pilfer anything it can get its hands on, even if those items belong to an ally. This Doppel is extremely greedy and refuses to give up anything once it has it in its possession.

cardSkill.name: Have a Halloween Night Boost!
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [IX] / Guaranteed Bewitch / Magia Seal Chance

selectableCharaList.description: The "Magical Girl born of Halloween". Or that's what she says at least... Karin loves reading and drawing manga so much that she's even created her own Magical Girl persona. She's heavily influenced by her favorite manga, Phantom Thief Magical Kirin.

charaMessageList.message:
I have so many fond memories of
Magical Kirin!

I want Alina-senpai to give me
some drawing lessons!

I'm Magical Karin,
savior of weak Magical Girls!

Halloween is special.
It's the day I came into being!

Thanks to everyone,
I found a new way to live my life!
I WILL save my grandmother!
Trick or... No, wait! Trick AND treat!
Now THIS is a Happy Halloween!
There's nothing this scythe can't cut down!
If you bring me candy next time, I'll let ya slide!
This is the power of a demon from the underworld!

selectableCharaList.name: Mitama Yakumo

cardMagia.shortDescription: Guaranteed Curse & Poison & Magia Seal (All Foes/1T) / ATK UP (Team/1T) / Curse (Self/1T)

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Guaranteed Curse+ & Poison+ & Magia Seal (All Foes/3T) / ATK UP (Team/3T) / Curse (Self/1T)

doppel.name: Doppel of Forewarning
doppel.title: Feature: Flower Petals
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel resents her environment and wishes to destroy everything. Her Doppel never forgets that death comes to all things equally. It covers everything with dancing flower petals and escorts girls elegantly with its white gloves. Like its master, it isn't able to attack directly, but its power, which is connected to the end of all things, is utterly terrifying - the magic of anything hidden under its flower petals rots away to nothing. The more the master relies on this Doppel, the closer her left arm will get to becoming completely one with it.

cardSkill.name: I Hope You Can Afford This♪
cardSkill.shortDescription: Heal [IX] / Damage UP on Enemies with Status Ailments [IX] / DEF DOWN [V]

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who operates as a Coordinator in the outskirts of Kamihama. Unable to fight for herself, she accepts Grief Seeds in exchange for items and providing magical adjustments. Though she usually has a sunny disposition and a friendly smile, very few Magical Girls know her true nature.

charaMessageList.message:
Hello!
What can the Coordinator do for you?

Are you here for an adjustment
Some items? A chat?
I'm sorry. Really, I'm only teasing you.

Just a warning,
you shouldn't take me lightly, or else!
Surely I'm destined to live a life of regret.
Yes, I love everyone, and hate everyone.

Wiping everything away
would feel so nice.
My my, not too shabby, if I do say so myself!
I'm so nervous, my heart is pounding...
Your Coordinator would appreciate a compliment or two!
Thank you, everyone, you're all a big help.

selectableCharaList.name: Tsukuyo Amane

cardMagia.name: Blizzard of Cherry Blossoms
cardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [V] / Damage After Using Charge UP (Team/3 Turns)

cardSkill.shortDescription: Damage After Using Charge UP [IX] / Critical Hit Chance [VII] / Connecting with Tsukasa will boost her ATK

cardMagia.name: Blizzard of Cherry Blossoms
cardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [VII] / Damage After Using Charge UP (Team/5 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Seclusion
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [IX] / Damage After Using Charge UP (Team/5 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Seclusion
doppel.title: Feature: Terrarium
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel isn't swayed by mood or emotion. She does, however, rely on her other half, the only person who truly understands her. Through this, the two of them are capable of completely isolating themselves from the outside. Together in their miniature world, they need only the company of the other to survive. This Doppel shuts out all physical and magical phenomena, allowing its master to perfectly protect herself and her twin. Though doing so causes their memories of anyone but each other to fade away.

cardSkill.name: Our Sound Resonates as One
cardSkill.shortDescription: Damage After Using Charge UP [XI] / Critical Hit Chance [IX] / Connecting with Tsukasa will boost her ATK

selectableCharaList.description: Tsukasa's twin sister, Tsukuyo hopes to liberate Magical Girls. Constant training in music, calligraphy, and dance has granted her considerable skills. Though she is admired by her peers, she doesn't have any friends she feels she can open up to. She can only be at peace when she is with her sister, Tsukasa.

charaMessageList.message: Are you my sister?
My father's flute held a secret.
Tsuruno Yui...and Felicia Mitsuki?!
She was strikingly similar to myself.
I never want to despise Tsukasa...
We're spitting images of one another!
Oh Mother, just who am I?!
We have triumphed!
Perseverance bears fruit once again.
Thank you for your attention.
Thus concludes our performance.

cardMagia.name: Pluvia☆Magica

doppel.name: Doppel of Mercy
doppel.title: Feature: Salvation
doppel.description: The master of this emotion tries to save all of existence. This Doppel appears as a huge floating Soul Gem. Once it is summoned, it creates an existence within which all things around it are consumed, and then takes control of everything within that existence. After that, it floats higher into the air and a shower of light arrows rains down. While all of this is happening, the master of this emotion sleeps inside the huge Soul Gem.

cardSkill.name: I'll Shoulder Your Burden
cardSkill.shortDescription: Heal [VIII] / Charges MP [VIII]

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl with extraordinary potential who lives in Mitakihara with her parents and younger brother. Gentle and caring, she is always surrounded by friends. She uses a bow and arrow in battle.

charaMessageList.message: Hmmm... Which ribbon should I wear?

I don't know much about this city...
It sure is strange, though...
I'm a Magical Girl…so I have to do this!
Is this…real?
Were you the one who was calling me?
Don't tell anyone in class, okay?
If I'm awesome, it'll all work out!
Thank goodness...it looks like we've won!
We did it! Great!
Yes! Looking good!
Phew... We made it through somehow!

selectableCharaList.name: Sayaka Miki

cardMagia.name: Prestissimo Agitato
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [V] / Survive (Self/3 Turns) / Guaranteed Critical Hit (Self/2 Turns)

cardSkill.shortDescription: HP Regen [VII] (3 Turns) / ATK UP [VII]

cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [VII] / Survive / Guaranteed Critical Hit / Guaranteed Counter (Self/2 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Unrequited Love
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [IX] / Survive / Guaranteed Critical Hit / Guaranteed Counter (Self/2 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Unrequited Love
doppel.title: Feature: Mermaid
doppel.description: The master of this emotion suffered from young love and chose a fate so harsh that she could not bear it alone. As such, the Doppel dreams of love while it swims effortlessly through the air, playing a song for its master from its vast hollow body. It can control several swords to attack its enemies with the soundwaves that emanate from its body, but as long as the master uses it, she cannot flee from the discontent that troubles her heart.

cardSkill.name: My Turn Now!
cardSkill.shortDescription: HP Regen [IX] (3 Turns) / ATK UP [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: A straightforward Magical Girl with a strong sense of justice. She is a dear friend of Madoka, who also lives in Mitakihara. She looks up to her Magical Girl senpai, Mami, and her fighting style of mass-conjuring weapons resembles hers. She used to visit her childhood friend Kyosuke in the hospital often.

charaMessageList.message: Never thought I'd be doing detective work!

I can't believe we're going to hang out
together again! Am I dreaming?

I wonder if I'll be able to find some
rare CDs in Kamihama.

To think there were so many
Magical Girls out there!
Why did it have to be us?

Alright, time to kill myself some
Witches today!

Magic really exists, and miracles
really do happen.
Case closed, I guess!
Sheesh, that was cutting it close!
Is it okay to praise myself for that?
I almost dozed off from sheer boredom there!

selectableCharaList.name: Mami Tomoe

cardMagia.name: Tiro Finale
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [VI] / Bind (All Foes/1 Turn) / Skill Surge (Team/1 Turn) / DEF DOWN (Self/1 Turn)

cardMagia.name: Tiro Finale
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [VIII] / Bind (All Foes/1 Turn) / Burn (All Foes/3 Turns) / Skill Surge (Team/1 Turn) / DEF DOWN (Self/1 Turn)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Invitations
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [X] / Bind (All Foes/1 Turn) / Burn (All Foes/3 Turns) / Skill Surge (Team/1 Turn)

doppel.name: Doppel of Invitations
doppel.title: Feature: Dressing Up
doppel.description: The master of this emotion doesn't trust it but battles on, regardless of its presence. This Doppel is very small compared to other Doppels and always sits on its master's head, so the master is hardly aware of it. It is doubtful that they communicate, so its master fights normally while it supports her. It is small and looks unreliable, but its vines are powerful enough to penetrate any enemy.

cardSkill.name: Tiro Duet!
cardSkill.shortDescription: Damage Inflicted UP [IX] / Guaranteed Bind / Guaranteed Burn

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who has been fighting Witches in Mitakihara longer than the others. She is experienced and takes care of Madoka and her friends. She is proud of being able to save people, and loves tea.

charaMessageList.message: This town is like a maze. I feel so uncertain...

Believe in yourself and fight.
The rest will follow.
Shall we have a tea break?
Being a Magical Girl is no walk in the park.

What dream do you intend to
make a reality?
What's going on in in this city…?
Oh… Could you beat me on equal footing?
One job done.
Phew... That was close!
All right then. Time for some tea.
Want to come to my place after this?

selectableCharaList.name: Kyoko Sakura

cardMagia.name: Kugatachi
cardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [V] / ATK UP (Self/3 Turns)

cardSkill.name: Just Can't Sit n' Watch
cardSkill.shortDescription: Blast Damage UP [VII] / Reduce Damage [VII]

cardMagia.name: Kugatachi
cardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [VII] / ATK UP (Self/3 Turns) / Blast Damage UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Desperation
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [IX] / ATK UP (Self/3 Turns) / Blast Damage UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Desperation
doppel.title: Feature: Warrior Actress
doppel.description: The master of this emotion doesn't trust its mysterious power, she only borrows its weapon and wields it herself. To the master, it's is no more than a hateful thing that drags up her painful past due to its power, a dubious hypnotic magic that controls mist to produce illusions. But even still, it possesses her regrets, hidden deep in her heart, so she allows it to aid her somewhat in battle, though she remains suspicious of it. The Doppel itself is the fluttering kimono-like thing, while the candlestick holder the master rides is a separate being altogether.

cardSkill.name: Just Can't Sit n' Watch
cardSkill.shortDescription: Blast Damage UP [IX] / Reduce Damage [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: Kyoko is a Magical Girl from Kazamino who doesn't seem to go to school or have a home. Defiant and pragmatic, she often butts heads with other Magical Girls. She wields a multi-jointed spear, and can create magical barriers. She is always snacking.

charaMessageList.message: Ya look like ya stress out real easy.
Naive Magical Girls get killed quick.
...Well, a free meal's a free meal.
I'm gonna survive no matter what.
I can't just ignore idiots like that.
If ya get it, then don't be a dumbass.
Substance over style, that's me.
I'll take the win, thanks!
Well that went well!
Now then. What to eat?
They're gonna feel that one!

selectableCharaList.name: Mito Aino

cardMagia.name: Thorn Arrow
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [V] / Guaranteed Taunt / Evade Chance (Self/1 Turn)

cardSkill.name: Time to Double Up!
cardSkill.shortDescription: Evade Chance [VII] / Taunt Chance [VII] / Critical Hit Chance [VII]

cardMagia.name: Thorn Arrow
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [VII] / Guaranteed Taunt & Evade (Self/1 Turn) / DEF UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Unity
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [IX] / Guaranteed Taunt & Evade (Self/1 Turn) / DEF UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Unity
doppel.title: Feature: Cloak
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel wishes for beautiful friendships to last for eternity. This Doppel answers that desire by compressing everything it captures into a single concentrated lump, which turns into an unbreakable crystal that will shine for thousands of years. Attacks by the Doppel are made by crystallizing its master's emotions, but continued use of this power causes even the master's memories to harden, making it impossible to create new ones.

cardSkill.name: Time to Double Up!
cardSkill.shortDescription: Guaranteed Evade / Taunt Chance [IX] / Critical Hit Chance [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: An innocent and carefree Magical Girl, Mito isn't afraid to be herself. She's usually laidback, but there are times when she says things that cut to the core. Mito lives in the same apartment complex as Leila and Seika, her two childhood friends who she truly treasures.

charaMessageList.message: We definitely have more fun together!
Look! Flowers are bloomin' over here!
It's fine! I just know it is!
Here ya go! You can eat these acorns!
Huh? I whistled and all the birds came!
Hopscotch! Into a...handstand!
Okay, first one to the corner wins!
Hm? Looks like I won?
Whew... I'm glad you're okay.
I wooon! I did win, right?
That was tough. I need some water.

selectableCharaList.name: Kokoro Awane

cardMagia.name: Surging Release
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [V] / Counter Chance (Team/3 Turns)

cardSkill.name: I Won't Hide My Feelings Anymore
cardSkill.shortDescription: Guaranteed Counter / Reduce Damage [VII]

cardMagia.name: Surging Release
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [VII] / Counter Chance (Team/3 Turns) / Reduce Damage (Team/3 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Restraint
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [IX] / Counter Chance (Team/3 Turns) / Reduce Damage (Team/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Restraint
doppel.title: Feature: Shell
doppel.description: The master of this emotion knows it's simply a way for her to release her pent-up frustration. She views it with mixed feelings, as she understands there are drawbacks. This Doppel sprouts thorns to resist those who would harm it and attacks ferociously when it senses danger. On rare occasions, the agitated emotional state of its master may cause it to explode, and its shell – though stronger than metal – will break and release a surge of powerful magic.

cardSkill.name: I Won't Hide My Feelings Anymore
cardSkill.shortDescription: Guaranteed Counter / Reduce Damage [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who always tries to put on a happy face. Her parents divorced when she was young, and she's lived with her father ever since. Their relationship has become strained, leading her to become emotionally shutoff.

charaMessageList.message: I just want her to realize one day.
She's not the least scared of dying!
I should have protected them!
I decided I'm going to live for myself!
You can't just let your family fall apart!
Can I stick with you?
Why...? Why did she leave?
Everyone okay? No one's hurt?
Whooo, what a rush! *Giggle*
Whew, it's over. What a relief.
Don't worry. I'll protect you.

selectableCharaList.name: Himika Mao

cardMagia.name: Meteor Punch
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [V] / Survive / HP Regen (Self/2 Turns)

cardSkill.name: Time for a Little Give and Take
cardSkill.shortDescription: Endure (3 Turns) / Blast Damage UP [VII]

cardMagia.name: Meteor Punch
cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [VII] / Survive / HP Regen (Self/2 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.name: Doppel of Dissolution
doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [IX] / Survive / HP Regen (Team/2 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Dissolution
doppel.title: Feature: Bonds
doppel.description: The master of this emotion finds a sense of security by entrusting the dormant desires in her heart to her Doppel, which keeps them held in check. It transmutes her ego into a sphere, while her ties and obligations to her family become snakes binding it tightly together in place. The sphere yearns for freedom, but the snakes confining it are the only things maintaining its form. Were it to wrest itself free, the sphere would burst and fly away...but the master would never allow that to happen.

cardSkill.name: Time for a Little Give and Take
cardSkill.shortDescription: Endure (3 Turns) / Blast Damage UP [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who drives a hard bargain. The oldest daughter in a family of 8, she helps run the household with her father since her mother passed away. Being with her family makes her as happy as can be, but to make ends meet, she's always scrimping and saving spare change.

charaMessageList.message: What do I like to read? My bankbook!
I'm not stingy! I'm a thrifty spender!
Whoa, I found 1 yen! Yayyy!
My special drink is sure to perk you up!
Woo hoo! I got this for 90% off!

The fridge door can only be open
for 3 seconds!
Sale day is a battle at the supermarket!
One victory! Thank you, come again!
Easy as that!
I'm undefeatable!
I have to get back home!

doppel.name: Doppel of Electronic Ordinance
doppel.title: Feature: Electrocardiogram
doppel.description: The master of this emotion uses powerful electrical signals to burn the ill will from its target's body, incinerating its personality along with everything else. Though they are horrified by this Doppel's power, they are also tempted to believe that murder such as this is the only way to put an end to all human ill will. This Doppel also has power over both life and death, and, when it appears, the master's body and soul split apart temporarily, leaving her soul meandering in the space between life and death.

cardSkill.name: Allow Me to Write the Next Part
cardSkill.shortDescription: Guaranteed Follow Up Attack if Target Survives / ATK UP [IX] / Guaranteed Evade

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl who has been shy since childhood. Feeling that life was painful, she blamed herself for her loneliness. It was her fellow Magical Girls that led her out of this despair. Though she's grown stronger mentally, she still has a timid side.

charaMessageList.message: It was more lonely than painful.
If only everyone had been kinder to me.
To me, it was shining and beautiful.
I failed to die… Again…
I will hold on to this hope...and live.
I'm never very good with words…
Please, voice. Come out just this once!
I did it! I...I won!
My heart…is still...pounding!
It's all about being alive, right?
My heart is pounding… because I'm happy!

doppel.name: Doppel of Retribution
doppel.title: Feature: Fox
doppel.description: The master of this emotion performs acts of vengeance against those she hates, using a variety of magic attacks. This Doppel is part of the Fox Trinity and represents retaliation. It is skilled in magic and can use will-o'-wisps to confuse its enemies. So long as their master's grudge burns on, not even water can extinguish them. The master will lose her ability to think logically while using the Doppel; instead, she will act purely on instinct and perform extraordinary acrobatics.

cardSkill.name: Allow Me to Handle This
cardSkill.shortDescription: Heal [VIII] / Accele MP UP [IX] / ATK UP [IX]

selectableCharaList.description: A Magical Girl raised in an orphanage. She came from an affluent family, but after her parents fell ill and died, she went to live in the Azalea House. A pro at everything she sets her mind to (except cooking...), she helps keep the other orphans in line.

charaMessageList.message: Hazuki, Ayame, follow me.
We'll survive this on our own, just watch.

Kamihama City...
Not half-bad for a hunting ground.
It's not that I'm trying to hide...

Hazuki, Ayame.
Let's go with our usual strategy!
Stay out of it. That one is our prey.
I'll take on every burden...
We're going to survive, just watch…
I keep my eyes fixed on the road ahead of me.
Yes... I guess that'll do.
Keep moving forward... It's all we can do.

doppel.name: Doppel of Adoration
doppel.title: Feature: Carnation
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is reluctant to admit that her Doppel represents her nature. It has the power to ensnare others' hearts and hold them under its sway. Anyone pulled in by this Doppel will be unable to resist its allure. Many of its victims will devotedly throw their lives away for it; others will find it hard to raise a hand against its loveliness. If she were to use this power to gain too many blind fanatics, however, she would bring about her own end.

cardSkill.name: Will You Stay By My Side?
cardSkill.shortDescription: Damage Inflicted UP [IX] / Charge MP [VI] / Accele MP UP [V]

selectableCharaList.description: A captivating Magical Girl who unwittingly attracts much attention from men. Her admiration of fatherly figures gives her a tendency to act unguarded around older men. Granted a love of art by her late father, she intends to work in art restoration and got a job at an art museum to realize that dream.

charaMessageList.message: I think Ria's mad at me again.
I want to stay together a little while longer...
Sayuki is here to see the sword exhibit.
Oh no, I forgot something back there.
Hmm, what did I do wrong?
I should ask Asuka for more training.
I like how you do that.
Hm? What? Did we win?
Pheeew... We won.
I tried my best!
Hee hee... I'm glad.

doppel.name: Doppel of Manipulation
doppel.title: Feature: Needles
doppel.description: The master of this emotion has vowed absolute loyalty to her savior. It penetrates enemy and master alike with sharp needles, sewing the fate of all things tight. This act represents its extreme devotion, such that it offers up everything, including its life to its benefactor, while symbolizing the perilousness of its dependence upon the other, which it cannot maintain its identity without. The sharper the needles are, the more the stitches there are, and the harder it becomes to extricate oneself from it. However, this merely serves as an expression of the master's desire.

cardSkill.name: This is for Oriko, Too!
cardSkill.shortDescription: Guaranteed Counter / Guaranteed Taunt / DEF UP [VII]

selectableCharaList.description: Oriko's loyal servant, Kirika is a dangerous Magical Girl who doesn't hesitate when acting for her queen, no matter how immoral the deed. She is known as the "Dark Magical Girl" but her mind is pure like a child's. She even has a sweet tooth like one.

charaMessageList.message: Oriko...so merciful, you always forgive me...
I became a Magical Girl to be with you.
I will use this power for you, and you alone.
Enough! Die and atone for your sins!
Oriko, quickly, give me orders!
Just ask, I'll be anything for you!
Ah...so this is what true love is like!
What? You're done already?
As to be expected.
Hey, that was actually kind of fun.
Don't underestimate my love.
